all-packages.description:
The &lt;b&gt;HTTP&lt;/b&gt; library.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
A lightweight HTTP library which allow to work with the
HTTP protocol either from the server (CGI under Apache)
or the command-line as http client or server.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
This library does not fully support Windows.
&lt;br&gt;
